name: Turbo Toad Prop House Community Voting Token

metadata.name: Turbo Toad Prop House Community Voting Token
metadata.description:
Turbo Toad Prop House Community Voting Token is a voting token designed to be used in the TURBO Prop House ecosystem. Proceeds from the sale of this token will be split; 20% to the artist, 80% to the TURBO Prop House Multi-Sig Wallet. 

The TURBO Prop House Multi-Sig Wallet will be managed by a team of builders representing various ecosystems and roles in both Turbo and NounsDao communities. 

The TURBO Prop House Team will create mechanisms to work with the community on round mandates and rewards. 

One token equals one vote. Builders do not need a token to submit proposals.
